getPSDELogicNodes.name: 获取完成需求数
getPSDELogicNodes.sql: select count(1) as stories from zt_story t1 where t1.deleted = '0'  and  FIND_IN_SET(t1.id,(select stories from zt_release where id = ?))

getPSDELogicNodes.name: 获取遗留的bug
getPSDELogicNodes.sql: select count(1) as LEFTBUGS from zt_bug t1 where t1.deleted = '0'  and    FIND_IN_SET(t1.id,(select leftbugs from zt_release where id = ?))

getPSDELogicNodes.name: 获取解决的bug
getPSDELogicNodes.sql: select count(1) as bugs from zt_bug t1 where  t1.deleted = '0'  and   FIND_IN_SET(t1.id,(select bugs from zt_release where id = ?))
